62469.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
62469.description: In a Halloween installment, the gang looks into strange disappearances in a spooky town. There, an old lady named Hama teaches Katara some secret Waterbending techniques.

62470.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
62470.description: On the eve of the eclipse, Aang's anxiety gets the better of him. His dreams become nightmares, and soon he can no longer tell dream from reality.

62471.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62471.description: SpongeBob and Patrick go back in time to see the young Mermaidman and Barnacleboy. // SpongeBob and Patrick watch their heroes fight bad guys in a classic Mermaidman and Barnacleboy episode.

62472.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62472.description: Squidward bets SpongeBob he can't go a day without crying. // Mrs. Puff has to work through her summer break at the Krusty Krab.

62473.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62473.description: Leo doesn't trust Slash when he emerges leading a team called the "Mighty Mutanimals".

62474.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62474.description: While the Mighty Mutanimals lay siege to TCRI, the Turtles must brave the bizarre world of Dimension X to save the enslaved people of New York.

62475.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62475.description: When a rhino comes to the Valley of Peace seeking to destroy the Dragon Warrior, Po tries to befriend him before he discovers Po's true identity.

62476.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62476.description: After Po unleashes an 'impossible move', he's told that the most powerful fighter in the Valley of Peace always turns evil, and that's him!

62477.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62477.description: When a sneeze from Rico causes the underground tunnel system beneath the zoo to rupture Skipper calls in 4 beavers to fix the situation. // Skipper's having one of those perfect days, and he decides to use the opportunity to settle an old score.

62478.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62478.description: When Doris the Dolphin shows up with Parker the Platypus and asks a favor of Kowalski, he instantly jumps to her rescue only to find out it’s to free her brother Francis who happens to be a “mind-jacked” Dr. Blowhole.

62479.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62479.description: When Squidward points out to SpongeBob that he's not normal, SpongeBob makes it his mission to become normal. // SpongeBob wakes up one morning to find that everyone in Bikini Bottom is gone - even Gary!

62480.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62480.description: While working at the Krusty Krab, SpongeBob accidentally gets a splinter. // SpongeBob and Patrick are having fun with their new slide whistles, and, of course, it's driving Squidward crazy.

62481.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62481.description: Everyone is in awe of Larry the Lobster's daredevil ways, especially SpongeBob and Patrick. // Everybody who's anybody is going to a big party in Bikini Bottom, but you have to be a certain shade of tan to get in.

62482.title: Nella The Princess Knight
62482.description: Sea Dragons threaten to spoil Castlehaven's Beach Day. // During a scavenger hunt, Smelgly is paired with Olivia, who takes advantage of their new friendship.

62483.title: Nella The Princess Knight
62483.description: Nella brings some wild critters to school for show-and-tell, but things soon get out of control. // Two rock giant brothers have a disagreement, leaving Nella's family carriage stranded on top of their bridge.

62484.title: Bubble Guppies
62484.description: Are you ready to rock? The Bubble Guppies are taking the stage with their guitars, drums and keyboards. Get ready to crank it up to 10 and learn about everything rock and roll.

62485.title: Bubble Guppies
62485.description: When Oona's friend Avi breaks a bone in his tail, he needs to visit the doctor. The Bubble Guppies aren't too worried - after they learn that it's a doctor's job to make everyone feel better.

62486.title: Dora the Explorer
62486.description: C'mon and join the musical parade! Dora and Boots are leading a parade over the Piano Bridge and through the Swinging Gate to free the instruments that were locked up by the evil Señor Shhh!

62487.title: Dora the Explorer
62487.description: Dora and her friends are super good at hiding, especially Señor Tucán when he hides in the Rain Forest. If we can find all 8 friends, Señor Tucán promises to introduce us to his new baby toucans.

62488.title: Rusty Rivets
62488.description: Rusty forgets the code to his robotic piggy bank, activating its self-defense mode and turning it into a runaway robotic boar. // Rusty and Ruby must save a baby whale that's been beached during a storm and reunite it with her family.

62489.title: Rusty Rivets
62489.description: New neighbor Frankie Fritz bot-naps Botasaur, making Rusty and Ruby go on a chase to get their friend back. // Rusty builds a machine that makes and stacks sand blocks, to help Liam build a giant sand castle.

62490.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
62490.description: When Blaze and Starla encounter a herd of cows wandering out in the desert, they must embark on a wild west adventure to bring them back to Starla’s barn.

62491.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
62491.description: It's the day of the Dragon Island Duel, a race around tropical Dragon Island! But when Crusher cheats and sends Blaze away before the race, AJ must set out to rescue his best friend and bring him back to the starting line.

62492.title: PAW Patrol
62492.description: Mayor Goodway calls on the Paw Patrol to rescue her twin niece and nephew from a tree, and then twin sit for the day! // Expecting the fireworks for Adventure Bay Day, Mayor Goodway receives a package of piglets after a mix-up!

62493.title: PAW Patrol
62493.description: Impressed by the Paw Patrol's rescues, Alex sets up his own mini-Patrol, recruitng Chickaletta, Cali, Turtle, and Bunny. // Alex loses his first tooth, then really loses it.The tooth must be located before the Tooth Fairy comes!

62494.title: PAW Patrol
62494.description: While camping, Marshall and the PAW Patrol help Alex learn about Fire Safety! // It seems like a regular day in Adventure Bay as the Paw Patrol is called to duty. But the pups are in for a surprise - PAW Patrol Appreciation Day!

62495.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62495.description: SpongeBob, while grocery shopping, discovers a "how to throw a party" kit. He decides to throw a big party and invites everyone he's ever known. Unfortunately for his guests, SpongeBob plans everything right down to the minute.

62496.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62496.description: SpongeBob and Pat want to make some extra cash so they decide to sell chocolate bars door to door. They have no luck at first. In fact, they end up buying more stuff than selling stuff. // Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy are visiting the Krusty Krab, and they get into an argument about whether or not Barnacle boy should be treated as the kid sidekick anymore.

62497.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62497.description: It's another day of boating school for SpongeBob, and this time, Patrick wants to come along too. Patrick becomes the new student in SpongeBob's class, and from his introduction, begins getting SpongeBob in trouble. // It's another day at the Krusty Krab when a random customer makes a purchase that causes Mr. Krabs to earn his one millionth dollar! To celebrate, he takes SpongeBob and Squidward on a clam fishing trip.

62498.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62498.description: The Penguins are faced with a global battle when their specialty food-making machine belches out a toxic cloud that threatens not just the zoo, not just the city, but the earth itself!

62499.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62499.description: King Julien is literally bounced out of his kingdom and onto the New York streets. A kindly old lady thinks he's a cat and swoops him up. He's encroaching on another's turf, though - the apartment's already home to a feline-impersonator, a female ferret named Zoe. Julien is taken with Zoe, and puts on his best seduction moves. Will the street-smart ferret succumb to his kingly charms? Smart money says... you never know! Action Reaction: Skipper is forced to live his worst nightmare when he's doused with Inflatium and stress causes him to blow up like a balloon. Guess what this means... no more going on missions! Sitting behind a desk doing paperwork instead! Hans takes advantage of the situation and targets a massive weapons lab, and without Skipper the penguins are easily captured. How can Skipper combat the evil puffin if he's in a puffy state?

62500.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62500.description: After Po unleashes an 'impossible move', he's told that the most powerful fighter in the Valley of Peace always turns evil, and that's him!

62501.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62501.description: After Po disobeys Shifu's orders, the Hierarchy of the Sacred Onyx Council replaces Shifu with a new master who banishes the Furious Five and plans to destroy Shifu.

62502.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62502.description: After encountering mutants and ninjas, Casey Jones decides to take on "pure evil" alone. When he meets Raphael, the two hot-headed fighters must put their dislike for each other aside and work together against a common foe.

62503.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62503.description: A fungus mutant spreading through the sewers causes the Turtles and April to experience their worst fears as Leonardo must face his greatest fear- losing his team.

62504.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62504.description: When his clarinet goes missing, Squidward must become a hardboiled detective to track it down. // Squidward sends SpongeBob and Patrick on an increasingly difficult scavenger hunt to get them out of his hair.

62505.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62505.description: SpongeBob's new friend is a giant fluffy hamster. There's one problem, though: no one else can see him! // Patrick wants to be a horse!

62506.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62506.description: Gary has a pet translation collar, and he's talking up a storm. Everyone loves it... except for Squidward! // When a small clown gets left behind by the circus, SpongeBob takes the hapless harlequin under his wing.

62507.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62507.description: After Po disobeys Shifu's orders, the Hierarchy of the Sacred Onyx Council replaces Shifu with a new master who banishes the Furious Five and plans to destroy Shifu.

62508.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62508.description: When Mantis returns to his hometown claiming to be the Dragon Warrior to impress his ex-fiancé, Po pretends to be his sidekick who doesn't know kung fu.

62509.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62509.description: Rico’s beloved doll, Miss Perky, has a new line of princess accessories! Joy! But in order for Skipper to reward the loco penguin with the new swag he must fill a marble jar (one marble in for good behavior, one marble out for bad.) How in the world is Rico supposed to behave and fill the jar when King Julien has kidnapped his dolly with the intention of marrying her?

62510.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62510.description: When the Penguins lose access to their favorite snack, popcorn, Skipper and crew leap into action to gain a new supply of the salty treat. // When a camera falls from the sky into the lemur habitat, Julien and Maurice argue about who will keep the shiny toy. But when Maurice disappears in the struggle, the Penguins are called in to find the missing lemur.

62511.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62511.description: Casey Jones thinks he can take on the criminal underworld on his own, but he soon finds himself in over his head.

62512.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62512.description: A new mutant called Muckman starts to gain notoriety as NYC's "Monster Hero".

62513.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62513.description: When SpongeBob's grandma gives him a kiss in public, the guys at work tease him about being a little baby. // Squid is so sick and tired of living between SpongeBob and Pat that he decides to leave Bikini Bottom and go someplace where everyone is just like him.

62514.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62514.description: Sandy is going into hibernation in one week and she wants to pack a million activities for her and SpongeBob to do together in that short time. // Mr. Krabs tells SpongeBob and Pat that it's okay to borrow things as long as you put them back. So SpongeBob and Pat borrow a balloon from the Bargain Mart and they accidentally pop it.

62515.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62515.description: SpongeBob and Pat are fascinated by the snow they see inside the Treedome and want to play in it, but sandy is hibernating for the winter. // One day, Gary starts following Pat around and SpongeBob can't figure out why. At first, it doesn't bother him, but slowly he grows more and more jealous and becomes determined to win Gary back.

62516.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62516.description: Shifu tells the citizens of the Valley of Peace that whoever can defeat Po before sunset will become the new Dragon Warrior. When Hundun hears of the challenge, he returns to the village to claim the title.

62517.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62517.description: After Po gets trapped in a hole, Fung helps him out and is owed a favor. Will it be a costly one?

62518.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62518.description: When the zoo installs web cams to bring in new visitors, Private accidentally becomes an Internet star. // Skipper accidentally causes King Julien to lose his beloved crown. The penguins go on a dangerous mission to retrieve the crown from the sewer.

62519.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62519.description: Sick of Julien's annoying presence, the penguins decide to take a vacation on The Moon. // After Marlene is frightened by a spooky noise in the night, she and Skipper travel down to the sewer below the zoo to find the source of the scary moans.

62520.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
62520.description: It is the Day of Black Sun and the group meets up with the invasion force."The day has finally arrived and Aang is ready to take on the Fire Lord. But they soon realize that things aren't going to go according to plan, and their surprise attack isn't so unexpected." Part 2 is "The Day of Black Sun, Part 2: The Eclipse."

62521.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
62521.description: Second part to "The Day of Black Sun, Part 1: The Invasion". The eclipse has started and the gang only has a few minutes to get into an underground bunker and find and defeat Ozai. Zuko confront his father and learn about his mother's banishment while Aang, Sokka and Toph fight Azula and her Dai Li agents.

62522.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62522.description: SpongeBob attempts and fails his driving test again, but a ragged and fed up Ms. Puff wants him out of her classroom so she makes up some bogus extra credit for him so he can pass the test. // When SpongeBob and Pat go to a jellyfishing convention, SpongeBob tries to join an exclusive, elitist jellyfishing club. Secretly, the club president thinks SpongeBob is not worthy.

62523.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62523.description: When Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy go away for the weekend, they ask SpongeBob and Pat to house sit for them. Inside the house, SpongeBob and Pat discover the evil super villain, Man-Ray frozen in a tank. // SpongeBob becomes an overnight stand up comedy sensation when he starts telling derogatory jokes about squirrels. At first, Sandy is a good sport, but soon people start treating her as if she really was stupid and smelly.

62524.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62524.description: Sandy and SpongeBob get into a fierce competition doing extreme underwater sports. The longer they compete, the more people they attract and soon SpongeBob has a small following who cheer him on. // SpongeBob and Pat visit the zoo and SpongeBob innocently toses a peanut at an oyster in order to rouse it. The oyster goes crazy and suddenly the authorities demand to know what could have caused this.

62525.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62525.description: The Shredder kidnaps and experiments on the Mighty Mutanimals.

62526.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
62526.description: Mikey and Casey are befriended by Mondo Gecko, a radical skateboarding reptilian kid.

62527.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62527.description: To impress his fan club, Po releases the Mongolian Fist Demon. Now he has to figure out how to defeat the Demon and save the village and his fans!

62528.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
62528.description: Po disobeys Shifu's orders and looks into the Mystical Mirror of Yin and Yang, creating two versions of himself: one good and one evil!

62529.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62529.description: When stuffed Mort dolls become popular at the zoo, Julien gets jealous and get them recalled. Unfortunately, the real-life Mort is accidentally sent back to the factory along with his plush replicas. // Maurice bribes the zoo animals to celebrate “King Julien Day” by offering them candy. Only Skipper refuses to go along, but still he’s unable to avoid the annoying day.

62530.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62530.description: Marlene discovers a lost egg, and asks the penguins to care for it and keep it safe. But King Julien is jealous, and wants to raise the egg to be his second in command. // When Skipper steals the batteries to Julien’s stereo, he sets off a wild chase around the zoo that gets both of them stuck in the habitat of an angry kangaroo.

62531.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
62531.description: The penguins compete against the lemurs in a game of capture the flag. This should be easy for the crack penguin team, but for some mysterious reason the lemurs keep beating them to the flag. // Mort is kicked out of the lemur habitat after he touches King Julien’s feet one too many times. So, the penguins take him in and attempt to break him of his foot obsession.

62532.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62532.description: SpongeBob and Patrick disturb the Flying Dutchman's slumber and he turns them into ghosts. // Squidward and SpongeBob have to share a locker.

62533.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62533.description: Mr. Krabs loses SpongeBob's fry cook contract in a bet with Plankton and SpongeBob is forced to go work at the Chum Bucket. While there, SpongeBob is so homesick that he can't even fry up a single patty. // When SpongeBob and Pat discover a pencil from the surface they begin to draw with it. Everything they draw, comes to life! Soon, they begin to do small, lame pranks on the neighbors.

62534.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
62534.description: Pat has a box and he won't show SpongeBob what's inside of it because it's a secret. SpongeBob can't believe Pat would keep something from him and he pretends not to care what's inside, but secretly it's driving him crazy. // Squidward's old High School rival comes to town and brags to Squid about his famous marching band. Feeling outdone, Squid lies and says he has a band, too.
